1. Open Hue

2. Create a file "hive_testing.hql" using nano or vi editor
	 use sg;
	 insert overwrite directory '/user/techshaj4510/techshaj_hive_table' select * from employees;
	
3. Copy hive_testing.sql to your home directory in hdfs
	 hadoop fs -copyFromLocal hive_testing.hql
	 hadoop fs -ls
	
4. Go to Hue and create new Workflows
	 Rename "My Workflow"
	 Drag Hive2 and select the path of hive_testing.hql
	
5. Save and Submit the workflow

6. Check hive_testing.hql file in user directory (/user/techshaj4510/techshaj_hive_table)
   hadoop fs -cat techshaj_hive_table/0*
